title: Bleach-Shippuuden Anime Flash
description:
A new generation image/video Anime Gallery Slideshow in Flash. You can get this running on your PC/Mac or Website to take control of your images and videos and keep anime fans coming back ;)


Some Features:

- Video Demo : swf file to be opened in browser.
- Community Link.
- Unlimited support of image/video galleries.
- Automatic Slideshow.
- Easy XML Driven Libraries.
- Help Files. 

Make sure to join the flash community to easily learn and create similar eye candies.
